{"tid":1421210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［建議］每日狙擊警察之前無答嘅無題","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:49:20.000Z","uid":175547,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68dfb8e6f3516137faffd2ea4475c6846e092e72","tid":1421210,"uid":175547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:22:03.000Z","msg":"唔知大家記唔記得，之前政府/警察啲記者會，都係無正面回答尖鋭問題：<br />\n例如 7.21 警察遲到39分鐘  8.4將軍澳打到呀伯見紅 等等<br />\n<br />\n之前班錄音機一直話咩「手頭未有資料，唔方便答」、「我唔係前線，唔知現場情況」<br />\n而家警察每日開記者會，咁就啱啦，日日問返佢個幾條問題，問到佢直接回應為止。<br />\n<br />\n佢答無資料就話佢效率慢，準備不足，要佢聽日答返；佢話唔係佢負責，就叫佢搵返負責嗰個人出嚟。總之佢點答都死。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日日追問，唔好俾佢拖延當答咗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然警察日日搞記者會，我哋除咗要有民間記者會打對台之外，亦要令警察係記者會上難堪"},{"pid":"858bc164f44d448147970c50a908447d39738e45","tid":1421210,"uid":175547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"推 巴絲整合問題，問到警察口啞啞"},{"pid":"07092fd86f074a8e8e2d6acbab1ba5add5cf21e1","tid":1421210,"uid":281418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"721！<br />\n呢個一定全港最關心，一路咬住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952834b2ed47ab0c0762d00ecdfb2c9233478c0b","tid":1421210,"uid":175547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"推 我哋要盡可能反擊林奠陰招！"},{"pid":"757601d84bf855b9d228f127b6734e4db8d77cfe","tid":1421210,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bd272c0dd27bb6e094da413fa41926187f485f2","tid":1421210,"uid":175547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:45:11.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68aee7a55a31a2bbb4033b8bcc32080b909826c1","tid":1421210,"uid":67377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl